Parse NTFS Master File Table (MFT) with MFTECmd
Learning Objectives
By completing this lab, you will:

Extract and parse NTFS Master File Table (MFT) data using MFTECmd
Analyze file records, metadata, and timestamps within the MFT
Understand the forensic significance of MFT artifacts
Interpret MFT output for digital forensics investigations
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of file systems and NTFS structure
Familiarity with Linux command line operations
Knowledge of digital forensics concepts
Understanding of CSV data analysis
